210
00:14:41,010 --> 00:14:43,870
Vieš predsa, ako vážne
Mi Do berie vyšetrovanie, nie?

211
00:14:43,870 --> 00:14:46,640
Vážne si myslíš, že by to len tak
odsunula stranou a šla na rande?

212
00:14:51,790 --> 00:14:53,380
Naozaj?

213
00:14:58,470 --> 00:15:00,280
Čo to robí?

214
00:15:15,040 --> 00:15:18,440
